article_title: Dontre Hamilton protesters regroup after Friday arrests
article_text: A study in the Mayo Clinic Proceedings says there is no solid proof that some drugs approved by the FDA are helping patients live longer or maintaining quality of life.

article_metadata.title: Photos: Dontre Hamilton protesters regroup after Friday arrests

og.description: Protesters meet at Red Arrow Park on Saturday and continue to press for charges against fired police officer Christopher Manney. A number of protesters were arrested Friday night after blocking traffic on I-43.
